\begin_layout Subsection
P-symmetry
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This is generated by 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha:e_{i}\mapsto-e_{i}$
\end_inset

 given a basis 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ e_{i}\right\} $
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $V$
\end_inset

.
 In Clifford algebras, this is called the 
