Then 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\epsilon=\omega=\Omega=i\sigma_{2}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
0 & 1\\
-1 & 0
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

This defines a symplectic bilinear form on 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{C}^{2}$
\end_inset

